-- Hynix Semiconductor Plans 2011 Capital Investment of About 3 Trillion Won
-- B y   S a e r o m i   S h i n
-- 2010-12-26T23:46:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-26/hynix-semiconductor-plans-2011-capital-investment-of-about-3-trillion-won.html
Hynix Semiconductor Inc. plans
capital investment of about 3 trillion won ($2.6 billion) for
2011, a company spokeswoman said, confirming a Seoul Economic
Daily report. The investment size could change depending on
market conditions, Park Seong Ae, a spokeswoman at Hynix, said
by telephone. That compares with 3.38 trillion won investment
this year, she said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Saeromi Shin in Seoul at 
